{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/deckbuilding.gif?t=1739038842\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ALL the deckbuilding!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A good amount of <strong>weapons</strong>!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some <strong>modifiers</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And a bunch of <strong>buffs</strong>!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine these the right way and you'll have some real fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Can't say numbers right now but there will be more content coming for the demo and full release!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/largenumbers.gif?t=1739038842\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">AND YOU CAN MAKE THEM LARGER!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I've seen millions of damage done, someone hit <strong>13 BILLION damage</strong> in a single turn! You're encouraged to <strong>break this game,</strong> and with <strong>multiplicative buffs</strong> this isn't hard to do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But you have to be quick! <strong>The target damage</strong> keeps increasing every turn. If you can't deal enough damage, well... you can guess what happens I suppose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/glitchworld.gif?t=1739038842\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLOIT the buffs you get!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The best strategy is to go with the flow. Try to play to the strengths of your buffs as much as possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These buffs define the optimal route for your run and when it all works together... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Oh, such a great feeling!  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/endlesspossibility.gif?t=1739038842\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Ok well it's technically not endless... but it's definitely enough to keep you entertained! :D  </i></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739038842","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/page.bg.jpg?t=1739038842","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/f7fc4d35e381de89208eebcea3e6053ba6d1be5e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739038842","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/f7fc4d35e381de89208eebcea3e6053ba6d1be5e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739038842","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/deckbuilding.gif?t=1739038842\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ALL the deckbuilding!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A good amount of <strong>weapons</strong>!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some <strong>modifiers</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And a bunch of <strong>buffs</strong>!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine these the right way and you'll have some real fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Can't say numbers right now but there will be more content coming for the demo and full release!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/largenumbers.gif?t=1739038842\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">AND YOU CAN MAKE THEM LARGER!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I've seen millions of damage done, someone hit <strong>13 BILLION damage</strong> in a single turn! You're encouraged to <strong>break this game,</strong> and with <strong>multiplicative buffs</strong> this isn't hard to do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But you have to be quick! <strong>The target damage</strong> keeps increasing every turn. If you can't deal enough damage, well... you can guess what happens I suppose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/glitchworld.gif?t=1739038842\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLOIT the buffs you get!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The best strategy is to go with the flow. Try to play to the strengths of your buffs as much as possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These buffs define the optimal route for your run and when it all works together... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Oh, such a great feeling!  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/endlesspossibility.gif?t=1739038842\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Ok well it's technically not endless... but it's definitely enough to keep you entertained! :D  </i></p>","developers":["Kristoff Red"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/header.jpg?t=1739038842","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Any Steam-compatible Linux Distro